   -----------------------------------
               MFRC522      Arduino
               Reader/PCD   Uno
   Signal      Pin          Pin
   -----------------------------------
   RST/Reset   RST          9     white
   SPI SS      SDA(SS)      10    lila
   SPI MOSI    MOSI         11    blue
   SPI MISO    MISO         12    green
   SPI SCK     SCK          13    yell
   SOUND_PIN
   SERVO1_PIN
   SERVO2_PIN
   HALT_PIN
   GO_PIN
*/


